data.description: We dare you to compare this great home. Almost 2800 sqftUpgraded kitchen with granite counters, tons of cabinets and a walk in pantry and a great big center island42'' cabinets and statinless steel appliances LVP flooring downstairsScreen porchCustom firepitHot TubPrivacy fenced yard backing to woodsGas fireplaceWalk in closets in bedroomsHuge master bedroom suite Alarm system with cameras Crown molding downstairsPendant lights in the kitchenWired for TV in the garageYou'll have a hard time finding a home at this price with these features.  This comfortable home has a open floorplan downstairs that includes a large welcoming foyer leading to a nice big greatroom and kitchen.   The kitchen overlooks the large living room featuring a gas fireplace &big dining area. Upstairs, there are 4 large bedrooms with big closets including 3 walk in closets.  The nice master suite features a luxury bathroom with a tub, separate shower and double vanity.  You'll be thrilled at the size of the master closet. There's also a loft/living area that could be great for a kids hangout.  Out back, you're going to have plenty of opportunities to relax or entertain with screened porch, or your professionally built stone fire pit with built in seating or your fun hot tub.  All this surrounded by a a private backyard that backs to a wooded buffer.   A neighborhood pool is available for residents. You are sure to be inpressed with this home.
